Library of Congress itself,

00:03:43.660 --> 00:03:44.960
the audio-visual collections,

00:03:44.960 --> 00:03:51.100
we have some 3.6 million audio
collections, sound recordings,

00:03:51.100 --> 00:03:56.360 position:56%
