sense of urgency important?

00:13:48.850 --> 00:13:52.270
It's important because the task
at hand, to quote the title

00:13:52.270 --> 00:13:57.830
of an <i>Atlantic </i>article, is <i>Saving
Historic Radio Before It's Too Late</i>

00:13:57.830 --> 00:14:01.530
M, a sentiment that was
