information that can save lives.

00:27:45.410 --> 00:27:48.980
Native people through the world
had little if any opportunity

00:27:48.980 --> 00:27:51.940
to hear their language
over the radio.

00:27:53.030 --> 00:27:56.360
Majority of cultures
dominated the airwaves,

00:27:56.360 --> 00:27:58.110
