00:27:58.110 --> 00:28:01.380
in supporting indigenous
cultures in any form.

00:28:01.380 --> 00:28:05.410
It is through tribal radio tribal
members can hear their language

00:28:05.410 --> 00:28:08.570
and possibly rescue
it from extinction.

00:28:08.570 --> 00:28:10.420
Since radio was an oral medium,

00:28:10.420 --> 00:28:15.020
