01:15:37.320 --> 01:15:38.800
And we hear that all
the time, you know.

01:15:38.800 --> 01:15:42.670
It's like, oh, my family's had
this home for six generations.

01:15:42.670 --> 01:15:45.140
Well, it's still Indian
land, you know.

01:15:45.140 --> 01:15:47.860
And we like to talk about, oh,
