for this country.

01:15:57.280 --> 01:15:59.220
No, you haven't always
fought for this country.

01:15:59.220 --> 01:16:01.320
Because this hasn't
always been an America.

01:16:01.320 --> 01:16:05.320
There are restaurants in Italy,
still pumping out biscotti,

01:16:05.320 --> 01:16:08.750
that are older than this nation.

01:16:08.750 --> 01:16:10.880
And we missed that in the language.

01:16:10.880 --> 01:16:17.210 position:56%
And that's, I guess, my part in this
is that the Native voice and lens

01:16:17.210 --> 01:16:20.590
and language, that's
what we're talking about.

01:16:20.590 --> 01:16:23.170
The preservation of some of
our languages that are on --

01:16:23.170 --> 01:16:27.420
