01:17:03.620 --> 01:17:06.810
This is what I said, but
that's not what I meant.

01:17:06.810 --> 01:17:10.650
And that was so interesting
to me that it was so fickle,

01:17:10.650 --> 01:17:14.400
it was so thin, and
it melts in water.

01:17:14.400 --> 01:17:16.720
And that was that -- that became --

01:17:16.720 --> 01:17:18.590
I, again, didn't plan
